data.description: ***3.25% Assumable Loan Available(Must qualify*** Completely renovated in 2021, everything from the roof to the HVAC, floors, decks, walls, all just 2 years old and in great condition! Open concept kitchen with granite counter tops & large island. Full basement with 2 additional bedrooms, a full bath, office, media & bonus room. Conveniently close to everything you could need. 10 minutes to either downtown Chattanooga or Hixson. The large level yard on nearly half an acre. Seller is licensed real estate agent.
